TextChange: only you know what you want in life. Your parents, the neighbors, your best friend, they have no idea what you want. They know what you choose to show them.  Only you know what can make you happy, and only you know what you want to achieve. They are your goals and dreams, and no one elses.\n => w

Happiness varies from person to person. What makes Jack happy may not make Jane happy, and vice versa. It is up to each individual person to figure out what makes them happy and work towards that goal. Even if Jack is focusing on himself and Jane is making other people happy.
